<p>Girly styles were grounded with sheer, papery organdy, clean-cut silhouettes and suiting in a neutral, milky palette.</p>

<p>Midriffs were paired with matching full skirts and offset with Western-inspired boots, while lightweight pajama sets in silk faille took luxury loungewear to another level.</p>

<p>In true Zimmermann fashion, attention to detail applies to every piece with cascading blooms and handstitched butterfly embellishments being unexpected but pleasant surprises. </p>

<p>Taking florals to the next level, laser-cut petal flourishes were carefully placed given the art a 3D quality.</p>

<p>Natural elements in the form of agate charm bracelets, leather rope belts and woven raffia separates gave the collection an earthy feel.</p>

<p>Known for their feminine aesthetic and delicate, soft silhouettes, even suiting was relaxed and teamed with lingerie.   </p>
